'''''Ndabaramukije!''''', ni Sinema ya Namibiya yasohotse muri 2017 iyobowe na Philippe Talavera kandi yakozwe nka firime ya Ombetja Yehinga (OYO)<ref>https://letterboxd.com/film/salute-2019-1/</ref>.   Irimo Adriano Visagie, Odile Muller, David Ndjavera mu nshingano zabo hamwe na Monray Garoëb<ref>https://namibinsider.wordpress.com/2018/08/08/salute-nominated-for-amvca-8-questions-with-director-philippe-talavera/</ref> . Iyi filime yibanze ku buzima bwa Carlito 'Kado', wakatiwe igifungo cy’imyaka itatu kubera uburiganya, asiga umukobwa w’umukobwa utwite kugira ngo yirwaneho ku isi.<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt15056864/</ref><ref>https://www.ombetja.org/news/salute</ref> 

Filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu Kwakira 2017 mu nzu yububiko. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.<ref>https://www.rapidlion.co.za/film2021-1/philippe-talavera</ref>  Ku ya 30 Ugushyingo 2019 muri Canal Olympia Ouaga 2000, i Ouagadougou, [[Burukina Faso|Burkina]] Faso, umukinnyi wa mbere Adriano Visagie yatsindiye igihembo cya Sotigui nk'umukinnyi witwaye neza muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>https://www.paff.org/films/kapana/</ref>.  Yatowe kandi nka filime nziza muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo muri 2018 Afurika Magic Viewers Choice Awards (AMVCA) ndetse no gutoranywa muri sida 2018 i Amsterdam<ref>https://neweralive.na/en/posts/amsterdam-beckons-salute</ref>.<ref>https://economist.com.na/35522/after-hours/locally-produced-film-to-get-international-exposure-at-aids-conference-in-amsterdam/</ref>   

